
### $Id$ ###

To install pyxser, extract the tarball content, then:

python ./setup.py --verbose clean --all
python ./setup.py --verbose build --force
python ./setup.py --verbose install

To build a debug install:

python ./setup.py --verbose clean --all
env CFLAGS='-Wall -Wextra -Wshadow -pedantic -std=c99' python ./setup.py --verbose build --force --debug
python ./setup.py --verbose install


Thanks for using and testing... enjoy pyxser ;)

